<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>🎬 YouTube 자동화 앱</h1>
            <p>YouTube URL을 입력하여 자동 재생을 시작하세요</p>
        </header>

        <main>
            <div class="input-section">
                <form id="urlForm">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label for="youtubeUrl">YouTube URL:</label>
                        <input 
                            type="url" 
                            id="youtubeUrl" 
                            name="url" 
                            placeholder="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=..." 
                            required
                        >
                    </div>
                    <div class="button-group">
                        <button type="submit" id="startBtn" class="btn btn-primary">
                            🚀 시작
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" id="stopBtn" class="btn btn-danger" disabled>
                            ⏹️ 중지
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="status-section">
                <h3>📊 상태 정보</h3>
                <div class="status-info">
                    <div class="status-item">
                        <span class="label">현재 세션:</span>
                        <span id="currentSession">없음</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item">
                        <span class="label">상태:</span>
                        <span id="sessionStatus">대기 중</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="status-item">
                        <span class="label">활성 세션 수:</span>
                        <span id="activeSessions"><%= activeSessions %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="logs-section">
                <h3>📝 실시간 로그</h3>
                <div id="logs" class="logs-container">
                    <div class="log-item info">
                        <span class="timestamp">[시작]</span>
                        <span class="message">앱이 준비되었습니다. YouTube URL을 입력하세요.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>⚠️ 주의: 이 도구는 교육/연구 목적으로만 사용하세요.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
